{"tid":2120972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「血庫告急」昨僅321人捐血　明起捐血可獲贈小食","createTime":"2020-07-23T04:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T06:50:43.000Z","uid":208505,"like":33,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f1c77e8ad3daecf907a7bca9b79983875a8851","tid":2120972,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:34:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200722/mobile/bkn-20200722164911639-0722_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200722%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200722164911639-0722_00822_001.html&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=dc1fc182\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200722/mobile/bkn-20200722164911639-0722_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我很想捐血,但有黃色飾物,我怕比人告/恐嚇  所以唔敢捐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上去Facebook打一打氣,話比佢地聽，總有30000黑警<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/hongkongredcross/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fhongkongredcross%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=054a4534\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/hongkongredcross/</a>"},{"pid":"1944c49fe319d6ad0bb62b1b8ec59958153ad085","tid":2120972,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f03741f988d02e9a928e544201ec7b101c6e56","tid":2120972,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53383f35bd58c298944c67011d8d088a3641f66","tid":2120972,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:35:08.000Z","msg":"變相賣血"},{"pid":"108c01b56c4a225fdc7af6fb9fc96c4c5af1c692","tid":2120972,"uid":123738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"賣少啲比支那啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再唔夠味搵班狗囉"},{"pid":"c91a1905c2aada755b9bc568c91b49eca0110d03","tid":2120972,"uid":78222,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"送黃色飾物我再考慮下"},{"pid":"8a3f4ca995fbe0dbc826d815a69f676aa6785972","tid":2120972,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:36:35.000Z","msg":"黃色飾物捐唔捐得？"},{"pid":"71ffdac7a7f5d22058a91bbf44a48b6e3f2a553a","tid":2120972,"uid":37389,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"30000黑警，當有2成虧到捐唔到，仲有24000個， 男性一年可以捐四次女性一年可以捐三次， 我當唔好要佢哋咁辛苦全部一年捐三次， 總共佢哋可以捐到72000包血/年，即係每日197包。<br />\n<br />\n點解唔向佢哋求援？ 紅十字會係咪扮藍，但骨子裏根本就嫌棄黑警啲血污糟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75133557738e7fc7a98246597fb49a650ab0c7a","tid":2120972,"uid":80503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:39:00.000Z","msg":"會被人拉 不了"},{"pid":"01b2558e37d86f84a4ec65090f0ef263dde6461d","tid":2120972,"uid":73569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c91a1905c2aada755b9bc568c91b49eca0110d03","tid":2120972,"uid":78222,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"送黃色飾物我再考慮下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"可以考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23931c551721c001d219e9d840bed3ab2d56c88c","tid":2120972,"uid":44243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:39:22.000Z","msg":"搵藍血人捐"},{"pid":"58a4f27416e2bc1cbe2862c7cfb9656c4d5d9367","tid":2120972,"uid":208505,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:39:22.000Z","msg":"香港爆發第三波疫情，近日更錄得首宗捐血者確診個案，紅十字會輸血服務中心昨日登記的捐血人數僅有243人，創一月出現疫情以來最低紀錄，只及正常日子的三分一。紅十字會輸血服務中心李卓廣坦言情況十分嚴峻，市民捐血情況較今年農曆新年剛爆發疫情的時候更低，他憂慮近日確診入院的長者個案急升下，血庫會供不應求，呼籲市民繼續踴躍捐血。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李卓廣表示，正常日子時，每日會有大約800至900人捐血，農曆新年時因剛爆發疫情，捐血人數一度跌至300，已屬很低水平，想不到昨日的捐血人數更跌破300。他認為與第三波疫情有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據中心記錄，7月初起，每日捐血人數不斷下降，近日政府推出更嚴厲防疫措施，市民減少外出，令捐血人數大跌。此外，由於不少私人企業都改變了工作模式，例如在家工作，令流動捐血隊出動次數大減，之前每日平均出動4隊，昨日只出動到1隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於有捐血者確診一事，他呼籲市民勿恐慌，因捐血站做足防疫措施，對捐血者亦有一定要求，例如需要無病徵及過去28日沒有外遊及接觸確診者等，捐血前亦會探熱。他指醫院每日都有大量病人需要輸血，近日多了不少確診長者入院，亦會對血庫需求上升，擔心若捐血人數持續下跌，血庫會供不應求。截至昨日，目前A型、B型、AB型及O型血的血庫存量約可維持7至8日。"},{"pid":"801af9af971c4c1563172d2692335c1741142b61","tid":2120972,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"支持公務員去捐 反正平時佢哋都係要服務市民"},{"pid":"dc2393451ade797f262ca0191468242d5deae6c9","tid":2120972,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:40:27.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"74bbd2cdf2928e652e5dcbe677306226437c78a8","tid":2120972,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"801af9af971c4c1563172d2692335c1741142b61","tid":2120972,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"支持公務員去捐 反正平時佢哋都係要服務市民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:40:34.000Z","msg":"叫30000個去啦"},{"pid":"97189b4ae111ec2a6a6d8a9a2b0622d0281296a0","tid":2120972,"uid":78222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"01b2558e37d86f84a4ec65090f0ef263dde6461d","tid":2120972,"uid":73569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c91a1905c2aada755b9bc568c91b49eca0110d03","tid":2120972,"uid":78222,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"送黃色飾物我再考慮下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"可以考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:40:47.000Z","msg":"考慮架炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔一定捐架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea51befb7c7845e1b3696b041a0b788ef0d127d","tid":2120972,"uid":43663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:40:52.000Z","msg":